{"tid":2066392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[中印衝突] 外媒：解放軍5死11傷","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T09:24:42.000Z","uid":23707,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"49f9a7206ec2056a3964fde9c939ce059e39b714","tid":2066392,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10a23e730dafb4fbbb44fe50a8a1e9c7b5169fe","tid":2066392,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453f1780421f49509fdcce95722871524b1d2afa","tid":2066392,"uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:02.000Z","msg":"中印邊境衝突3印軍被殺 解放軍傳5死11傷 華外交部斥印方越界<br />\n<br />\n中印兩國近日關係緊張，印度軍方周二（16日）證實，一名高級軍官及兩名士兵在拉達克地區與解放軍衝突時陣亡；外媒消息則指，解放軍方面5死11傷。中國外交部同日回應，印方周一（15日）越過了具有爭議的邊界，並攻擊中方人員，引發雙方衝突。據了解，這是自60年代以來，中印首次在邊境衝突中出現軍人死亡。"},{"pid":"44d50d25e418d0c943c1e5f8539c9ecdf1a8dc50","tid":2066392,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:43.000Z","msg":"印度軍方發聲明表示，周一晚中印雙方曾經發生激烈戰鬥，釀成傷亡，死者包括一名高級軍官。報道指，這是中印雙方近日在邊境對峙以來，第一次出現人員傷亡。不過印度軍方稱，兩國高級別軍官正在會晤，以緩和局勢，但沒有做出進一步解釋。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅表示，印軍周一兩度越過邊界並作出挑釁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，還攻擊中方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，導致了雙方邊防人員爆發嚴重肢體衝突。中方敦促印方約束邊境士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，避免作出導致邊境形勢複雜化的單邊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"8344924691e9a0a6dee2e3968230db2ddba7111a","tid":2066392,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"石仔掉死？"},{"pid":"e4072388c3016e76f495ccb741f1a606a204c63e","tid":2066392,"uid":128287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"呀差加油"},{"pid":"a74ce9ce4379c08da42da111238e4b269dc0c855","tid":2066392,"uid":124616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"印度加油"},{"pid":"0b0592f02b933bb97daee92ece8e2e1d44d31960","tid":2066392,"uid":328114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"冇撚野下話，摺被軍都殺到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd9f5c518773f3935cacbfbd887e9c6f175f53a","tid":2066392,"uid":29153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"懲華反擊戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2b548c6e01f389d6ee2006c51e4ec990d637cd","tid":2066392,"uid":227366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"想知總共有幾多人打拳頭交<br />\n傷得咁少"},{"pid":"21b22e0e80847050ecfcd1fe9b309d6b1cdbbedf","tid":2066392,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"Yoga fire!!!"},{"pid":"650e16b2952e65a2318667e417965c7b96cc012d","tid":2066392,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"Yoga fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246a9bc45251f9079b70015afc5b5991880d699d","tid":2066392,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:59:18.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf7e64bee067